  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nFrom user report:\r\n```\r\nStatus do not support costume chain for loading gas fee now.\r\n1.Get in Dapps on any binance smart chain\r\n2. it cannot do anything because loop loading gas fee.\r\nLoad gas fee and do transaction normally\r\n```\r\nNetwork fee is not calculated at attemt to send tx now, but it was calculated in release 1.15 (before EIP-1559)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nCan see that Gas Limit and Gas price is calculated\r\n![IMAGE 2021-10-04 20:38:38](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/135905992-759cc159-a32c-43e1-ade4-0306f6edbabe.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![IMAGE 2021-10-04 20:42:20](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/135906469-23ae9bd2-8bb4-499f-b116-1bd344927173.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) Go to profile > Advanced > Network\r\n3) Add custom network with params:\r\nRPC URL: https://bsc-dataseed.binance.org/\r\nChain ID: 56\r\n4) Connect to network\r\n5) Try to send any tx\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n[status_logs.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/7280529/status_logs.zip)\r\n```\r\nWARN [status-im.ethereum.json-rpc:253] - :json-rpc/error eth_feeHistory :error {:code -32601, :message \"the method eth_feeHistory does not exist/is not available\"} :params [101 \"latest\" nil]\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
